  "title": "Production Supervisor (Semicond, Up $4500, Woodlands)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: Woodlands</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Euro MNC</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Salary: $3000-$4500</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Industry: Semicon industry</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervise day-to-day activities of production. Provide guidance to ensure that production and quality goals are met and plant rules are enforced.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all products are produced within quality guidelines and manufactured as per schedule.</li>\n  <li>Identify, recommend and help implement means to improve area’s operation, including quality enhancements, safety improvements, employee development,efficiency improvement and cost reductions.</li>\n  <li>Co-ordinate with NPI team to ensure First articles are shipped on time</li>\n  <li>Prepare and submit all required reports especially production schedule report on a timely basis.</li>\n  <li>Need to monitor manufacturing cycle time,ensure the efficiency targets of all production technicians is met</li>\n  <li>Need to ensure the Daily/weekly and Monthly O/p targets are met</li>\n  <li>Monitor scrap and ensure is within the targets</li>\n  <li>Co-ordinate with Buyer/Planners for shortage of materials and production schedules</li>\n  <li>Work with Equipment maintenance team in automation projects and ensure daily output of the equipments is met</li>\n  <li>Plan for Overtime of production team depending on production schedules</li>\n  <li>Co-ordinate with process Engineering team on daily process issue and improvement projects</li>\n  <li>Ensure production team is cross trained for optimum use of Technicians</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in Engineering related field</li>\n  <li>Minimum of 2 years supervisory experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>*Only shortlisted candidates will be notified*</strong></u></p>\n<p>Please submit your updated resume in MS format by using the <strong>APPLY NOW BUTTON.</strong></p>\n<p>Alternatively, you may also email your resume to us at <a href=\"mailto:emily.fong@atomrecruit.com\"><strong>emily.fong@atomrecruit.com</strong></a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Emily Fong</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Senior Talent Specialist<br>\n</strong>Atomrecruit Pte. Ltd. | MOM EA License No.: 15C7443<br>\nEA Personnel Reg No.: R1768368</p>\n<p><br></p>",
